title: The Trouble with Larry
description: Petunia invents an imaginary friend to help her always get her way.

title: La Revuelta
description: Darwin siente pena por los objetos del hogar en Elmore y los motiva a alzarse.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Camp Unikitty
description: The gang's set for an awesome weekend of glamorous, easy-living camping out in fun, friendly nature! But when Hawkodile challenges their idea of camping (it should be a fight for survival in the hostile woods), the gang switch places, with Hawkodile living a luxurious glamp life while Unikitty and the others survive in the wild. Will Unikitty still believe the "great outdoors" are all that great if they meet their doom by natural causes?

title: Te Quiero Mao Mao
description: Un solitario explosivo y su mejor amigo holgazán se desvían del viaje que los llevará a convertirse en leyenda y descubren que su historia apenas comienza.

title: Goodbye and Good Riddance
description: Summer's over and Ben is back at school. Unable to tell anyone that's he all these cool aliens that they've heard about all summer, Ben suddenly realizes he's gone from a "hero" to a "zero", that is until Vilgax comes after him with a vengeance. Ben must now reveal his hero side to his parents and to his fellow classmates. In doing so he saves his town and teams up with his dad to destroy Vilgax once and for all. But there is some bad news...Gwen has switched schools and is in Ben's class!

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Diminishing Discourse
description: Elliott and Frankie decide to tell Mo about what really happened to the dinosaurs.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: An UnbeLEAFable Day
description: While the trains are setting up for the Vicarstown Fall Festival, Thomas is feeling down about the end of summer and the changing weather.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Ultracolosal
description: Colosal se vuelve enorme para destruir a un monstruo altísimo, pero cuando se rehúsa a volver a su tamaño normal, el reino se enfrenta a un nuevo terror… el apetito insaciable de Colosal.

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Together Alone
description: Steven throws a party to bring his family together.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Elements Part 4: Cloudy
description: Before they can restore Ooo, Finn and Jake will have to escape exile in an endless sky.

title: Magic Act
description: Pocoyo is doing a magic show. He expects everyone to watch very carefully and take him very seriously but unfortunately his tricks don't quite go to plan and his friends all laugh. They're really enjoying the show. They think Pocoyo is great at being a funny magician. But that's not what Pocoyo wants to be - he wants to be taken very seriously - so he goes off in a huff. In the meantime, Pato, Elly and Baby Bird go around Pocoyo-land to tell everyone about the magnificent hilarious magician whose show they enjoy so much. As Pocoyo sulks, his friends gather around him, excited to see his tricks. Pocoyo is overwhelmed that his friends liked his show so much. He does some more tricks and his friends are thrilled.

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Melissa the Hero
description: Melissa brags about helping Petunia to the point of self-aggrandizement.

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: #AllAboutZee
description: Zee Zatara is flattered when she meets an overeager admirer named Casey Krinsky, but soon realizes that "her biggest fan" wants much more than just an autograph.

title: The Little Mer-Bear
description: In order to live under the sea the Bears must transform into mermaids.

title: #BreakingNews
description: Lois Lane's attempt to get an internship at the Daily Planet leads to her trying to unmask the Super Hero Girls, which forces the girls to a battle of wits with their greatest nemesis yet.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: The Revolt
description: Darwin tries to highlight the plight of all the household objects he feels are being oppressed and maltreated by the uncaring residents of Elmore. He then decides to lead those objects in a revolt against the townspeople.

title: Tunnels
description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Once Upon a Townsville
description: When a dainty princess on a mission comes to Townsville, the girls must learn the superhero way isn't always the right way.

title: The Inquisition
description: The students of Elmore Junior High find their world turned upside down when the mysterious school superintendent comes to stamp out their cartoonish ways. But who wants to be normal? Certainly not Gumball and Darwin.

title: Makes Zen to Me/Say Uncle
description: Makes Zen to Me: When Buttercup gets a fortune cookie saying peace lies within, the most violent of Powerpuffs sets out on a quest for inner peace./Say Uncle: The girls' go to pick up the Professor's brother at the train station, but mistake him for a wild-man being transported to the circus.

title: Mao Mao's Bike Adventure
description: When Mao Mao underestimates enemy and friend alike, it almost costs him the entire kingdom.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Attack the Block Party
description: Clarence, Jeff and Sumo investigate a high school party down the street, which they mistake for an alien invasion.

title: I See Turtles
description: Eileen and the gang want to see baby sea turtles hatch and go into the ocean.

title: The Sunflower
description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

title: El Corazon
description: El señor Robinson intenta recuperar la amistad de Gumball y Darwin y falla una y otra vez.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: El Poder Interior
description: Masato Kazami vuelve junto con los guardaespaldas de la familia para llevar a Shun a Japón, pero esta vez, Shun y Hydorous tienen una sorpresa preparada.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

description: Manzana y Cebollín se esfuerzan por subir a la montaña rusa más loca del parque de diversiones.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Gar Trains Punching Judy
description: With a big fight coming up, Punching Judy turns to KO and Gar to help her prepare.

title: Melancholic Megalomaniac
description: Elliott and Mo try to cheer up Lord Kallous, with the help of someone from his past.

title: A Sticky Situation
description: Sticky Joe's search for a can opener leads to a series of wacky adventures.

title: Steam Fight at the OK Corral
description: When Kevin convinces Steam Smythe to adopt a modern approach in fighting Ben, our young hero must resort to old-fashioned thinking to save the day.

title: Ocean
description: Blippi's trusty BlippiMobile safely transports him to a whole new underwater world! He dives into the sea, where he gets an ocean tour from a local resident, Jerry the Jellyfish. They swim through a huge kelp forest, explore the ocean floor and meet interesting underwater creatures along the way!

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Las Dos Espadas
description: Para escapar de la prisión del Hechicero Calavera, los Ninjas debe convencer a los Munces y a Geckles de que dejen de discutir y trabajen juntos.

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: #LivingTheNightmare
description: When Zee's friends are held captive in their nightmares by a dream demon, she'll have to confront her own hidden insecurities, or risk the Super Hero Girls being trapped in a prison of their own fears forever.

title: La Celula Nucleo
description: Los Fantásticos defienden la Célula Núcleo de un ataque de Tiko, y en el último intento de Dan por salvarla, él y Drago logran liberar un nuevo poder.

title: Undercover Grandmother
description: When Chata is blamed for a bad painting restoration, she must go undercover to find the real perp and clear her name.

title: The Powerpuff Girls: A Documentary/Girls Gone Mild
description: The Powerpuff Girls a Documentary: A film student attempts to do a documentary on the Powerpuff Girls and learns catching these superheroes at rest is harder than he thought./Girls Gone Mild: When Parents Against Powerpuffs tell the girls that their superheroics are becoming too imitable, the girls must hold back on fighting crime.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Park Managers' Lunch
description: The park guys want to make sure Benson gets back safe from his lunch with Gene.

title: El club de los solitarios
description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Cool for Cats
description: Sylvester believes a commercial that says eating Chewy Chomps will make him cool.

title: The Heart
description: When Mr. Robinson accidentally let slip how little he cares for Gumball and Darwin, they react by giving him the cold shoulder.  Surprisingly Mr. Robinson misses them and tries to win back their friendship. After a few failed attempts, Gumball and Darwin realize that Mr. Robinson's heart is protecting him, so they give it an intense affection overload.

title: The Imposter
description: Vic and Val are hot on the trail of some crucial intel that will expose Tez. There's just one problem, an incognito Mime is set on ensuring the information never sees the light of day.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: Silent Treatment/Sweet "n" Sour
description: The Silent Treatment: When the girls go to see a silent movie with the Professor, they end up getting pulled into the film by an old-time villain./Sweet 'n' Sour: The girls must figure out how to beat Townsville's newest band of criminals: a group of adorable little animals.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Escapism
description: Steven uses his psychic powers to find help.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: New Jersey
description: After donning a brand new Jersey, JP is recruited by the Hockey Kids! The only way to get JP back is for Craig and Kelsey to hit the ice!

title: La Sed de Poder
description: Tras una discusión entre Wynton y Dan, el coronel Tripp controla la mente de Wynton para que ataque la ciudad con Lupitheon. Esto inicia una guerra entre Los Fantásticos y el ejército.

title: KO's Health Week
description: KO spends a week dispensing healthy tips to everyone in the plaza.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Uncle Caveman
description: In this prehistoric-themed episode, Uncle Grandpa must save his new friend, Mr. Gus, from a hoard of hungry cavemen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Las Decisiones
description: Darwin finalmente se cansa de los consejos de Gumball y busca un nuevo mentor.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Decisions
description: When everything goes wrong in Darwin's life, he begins to suspect that Gumball's bad influence might be to blame. Darwin decides to go elsewhere for guidance and finds a new mentor in Alan. But maybe it's time Darwin started making his own decisions.

title: El Baul de los Recuerdos
description: Al ser confrontada por China Riot, Lia logra evolucionar a Pegatrix cuando comprende la verdadera razón de su obsesión por las cámaras.

title: Duck Lips
description: After Uncle Grandpa molds her mouth into duck lips, a young girl must face the consequences of her new found popularity.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Sad Sax
description: Mordecai wants to get back together with C.J.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Too Hot to Handle/The Big Squeak/Big Jumping Spider
description: Findley can't resist some freshly baked cookies that are too hot to eat./ Avocado's new toy is driving everyone crazy with its noisy squeaker./ Lucas performs epic jumps all around House./ Findley is nervous and wishes Lucas wouldn't jump.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: No Honor Among Bros
description: Rook is under the influence of Fistrick's "bro" essence, and starts to act like a bro. Can he and Ben infiltrate an alien fight club to claim the Golden Fist? (Introducing Slix Vigma, alien promoter.)

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: Kabooms Part 1
description: The Titans are excited to see the movie version of their favorite show "Babies vs Dogs".

title: Malos Actores
description: Alguien expone a Dan por mentir acerca de la evolución de Drago, mientras el equipo se enfrenta a Duran Dane y su desdichado Bakugan, Nillious.

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: Huracan Chata
description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

title: Kabooms Part 2
description: Inspired by the "Babies vs Dogs" movie, the Titans decide to make a big Hollywood film of their own.

title: Elements Part 1: Skyhooks
description: Upon returning to Ooo, Finn and Jake discover that there have been some radical changes in their absence.

title: Elements Part 2: Bespoken For
description: Ice King weaves a tale filled with drama, romance, and men's fashion.

title: Accidents Happen Boo Boo Song
description: Ella falls over, but Heidi the Horse teaches her to get right back up again!

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: My Name Is Jose
description: The Titans have Raven give them new super powers but have a hard time adjusting.

title: Hogar, Dulce Hogar
description: Los Fantásticos vuelven a casa y se dan cuenta de que el tiempo no ha pasado. Pronto descubren que su conocimiento acerca de las batallas ha aumentado de forma exponencial.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: Man Up 2: Still Man-ing
description: When someone steals all the water in Townsville, it's up to the girls to race through the Townsville Wastelands to get it back.

description: Finn and Jake infiltrate the new Slime Kingdom and are drawn into a heated skate battle.

title: The Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

description: Bing and his friends are at Amma's creche today making Eggy Heads! Amma explains that Eggy Heads need 7 sleeps, water, light and patience to grow it's cress hair. But Bing has an idea to help his Eggy grow cress hair quicker...

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: La Aventura de la Moto de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao subestima por igual a sus enemigos y a sus amigos, por poco le cuesta el reino entero.

title: Getting Truffy with It
description: Truff is happy. He has found a necklace that makes him even Truffier! Except he had no idea the necklace belongs to Starmush. And the Mushelder promised there will be consequences for whoever took it. Mush-Mush, Chep and Lilit now have to save Truff from being consequenced.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: What Rhymes with Omnitrix?
description: At a poetry slam event, Charmcaster's reading of Kevin's poetry causes magical trouble for Ben and Gwen, causing mind swaps that have everyone confused as to who's fighting who.

title: El Atrapador
description: Dan y Wynton se encuentran con la posible ubicación secreta de la Célula Núcleo, y con el coronel Tripp, que busca apoderarse de la fuente de energía.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dark Plaza
description: KO and the heroes of the Plaza fight to save Lakewood Plaza Turbo with everything on the line.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Little Sword of Horrors
description: Prohyas grows a new Magisword from a tiny seed, but doesn't know that his Carnivorous Plant Magisword is a menace to Lyvsherian society until its too late!

title: Body Swap
description: Fed up with their home experiences, Craig, Kelsey and JP agree to switch bodies!

title: Lightning Bark
description: Fung and Miff have come across a rare piece of bark struck by lightning. Chep desperately wants to add it to his collection, but Fung and Miff have no intention to give it to him. Now remembering every time Chep has been nice to them, Fung and Miff end up doing something they never thought possible…

title: Frenemy
description: When the coolest girl in school befriends the girls, she charms them into becoming her accomplices in a series of adventurous crimes.

title: Biggest Fan
description: An obsessed super fan goes to dangerous extremes just to be saved by her Warrior heroes: Vambre and Prohyas.

title: The Cone-versation
description: When Noah is forced to wear a cone of shame, he feel left out of everything. But when he learns of a pirate treasure buried under the school he becomes the leader of the team that goes on the quest to find it.

title: La Aventura Perfecta
description: Cuando a Mao Mao se le antoja vivir la aventura perfecta, Adorabat dice una mentira piadosa.

title: Mordecai and Rigby Down Under
description: Mordecai and Rigby have to catch a flight to the USA.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Splash Zone
description: Mayor Foghorn Leghorn hires The Looney Builders to build a giant water slide for Looneyburg's waterpark. He keeps adding onto the design with the support of Bugs until problems arise.

title: The Perfect Pitch?
description: Having watched everything on TV, the Titans decide to make their own show.

title: And Then There Were None
description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

title: Ramen
description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

title: OK A.U.!
description: An evil warlock takes our heroes to a strange alternate universe.

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: Unfairgrounds
description: Unikitty and her friends have an exciting day at their favorite amusement park/carnival boardwalk but Frown and Brock are there to ruin their good times and drive everyone out! The park owner warns Unikitty that if attendance keeps dropping the pier ​will close forever! Can the friends take charge, save the park, and find out Master Frown's secret ​motives? What a roller coaster of emotions!

title: Elements Part 3: Winter Light
description: Finn, Jake, and Ice King travel to the new Ice Kingdom to confront the person responsible for turning everything topsy-turvy.

title: No Sleep Sleepover
description: It's a sleepover at the castle and Unikitty and Puppycorn want to stay up all night, believing something magical must happen if you stay up long enough.​ At first the friends are game to stay up all night, but as they fall asleep one by one, Unikitty worries they won't make it! How far will she and her bro go to stay awake, and will they discover the secret reason people are supposed to go to bed when the Sandman shows up?

title: La ninera
description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

title: Time Crimes
description: When Clarence is convinced he has the power to manipulate time he vows to only use his abilities for good. However, a day at school puts his morals to the test when he's given the ultimate choice to help his friends or pause time in the name of fun.

title: Kabums Part 1
description: Los Titanes están ansiosos por ver la versión cinematográfica de su programa favorito, "Bebés vs. perros", hasta que la presentación de la película hace que se vuelva superaburrida de ver. Para salvarla, los Titanes se meten en la película e interrumpen la charla con mucha acción fascinante.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: Rad's Alien Sickness
description: When our heroes are infected with a virus, Rad stubbornly refuses to back down.

title: Misfortune Cookie
description: After receiving an ominous fortune, Uncle Grandpa must snoop out whom among his friends is an enemy in disguise.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: En la Oscuridad
description: La princesa Vania revela una entrada secreta que conduce a una mina subterránea bajo Shintaro donde se guardan los oscuros secretos de la ciudad.

title: Some Luck
description: While the Bears are transporting a Whiffle Wizard to a distant meadow, Good Luck seems to have a run of bad luck. His belief in his own bad fortune causes him to lose confidence, causing ever more "bad luck." It's only when he understands that we make our own luck that his "luck" changes.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple decides to help Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Escape from Beyond the Cosmic
description: When Clarence accidentally breaks a local arcade game Jeff has become obsessed with, Clarence puts together his own real-life version of the game at home, encouraging Jeff to act out his fantasy in levels created exclusively by Clarence.

title: Dia de elecciones
description: En un esfuerzo por demostrarle a Master Frown que no es una tirana, Unikitty acuerda celebrar una elección para ver quién será la nueva princesa del Unireino. En una situación sorpresiva, Master Frown toma una ventaja temprana en las encuestas. Unikitty descubre que Frown gana porque está haciendo trampa. ¿Recurrirá Unikitty a sus propios trucos sucios para ganar las elecciones o permanecerá fiel a sí misma y seguirá tratando de ganar gracias a su amabilidad?

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: No Me Agradas
description: La batalla de Ben y Gwen contra Kevin 11 en las redes sociales se convierte rápidamente en una guerra sin cuartel en la vida real.

title: Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 Part 1
description: Ben, Max Ben and Gwen investigate a couple of daring break-ins, only to discover they were both once secret Plumber installations. What our heroes find out is that those responsible for the break-ins are working for The Forever King. He's brought together a rogue's gallery of some of Ben's most notorious enemies to eventually steal the world's most powerful energy source...located deep inside the Plumber bunker at Mount Rushmore.

title: Juego Terminado
description: Unagami entra al mundo real y aterroriza a la ciudad de Ninjago mientras Jay, Zane y Pixal intentan evitar el desastre reuniendo a Unagami con Dyer.

title: Bath Song
description: Ella gets covered in mud so she goes into Mei's farmhouse to have a bath.

title: Viral Spiral
description: When the Amoeba Boys wreak havoc on the internet, Bubbles has to hack her sisters in to stop them.

title: Me Llamo Jose
description: Raven les da nuevos superpoderes a los Titanes, pero a ellos les cuesta adaptarse.

title: Germ Factory
description: After seeing Leshawna enjoying a sick day at home with ice cream and TV, Duncan convinces the other kids try to get sick too.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: Pocoyo's Puppet Show
description: Pocoyo finds a puppet theatre and some puppets. Brilliant! Time for him to be a puppeteer. He puts on a show for Caterpillar and Baby Bird. They love it, especially when the puppets do funny things like fall over. They bring Pato and Elly along to watch the show too. When Pocoyo makes fun of Pato and Elly with the puppets, Pato and Elly are nonplussed. They don't think it's so great to laugh at people. Pocoyo realizes that his show has upset his friends. He says sorry and explains he didn't mean it. Everyone makes friends again!

title: Los Mejores Amigos
description: Cuando el mejor amigo de Gumball regresa a la ciudad, Darwin se pone celoso.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Una Extrana Conexion
description: Drago lidera a los Bakugan contra la amenaza de Tiko, para proteger una poderosa fuente de energía.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: Ultraclops
description: Badgerclops gets huge to destroy a towering monster, but when he refuses to shrink down, the kingdom faces a new terror.

title: In Bugs We Trust
description: Bugs uses the babies' money to buy different toys than he promised.

title: I Don't Like You
description: Ben and Gwen's social media battle with Kevin 11 quickly escalates into an all-out war in real life.

title: Pelea de Vapor en el Corral
Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Weapon XI Part 1
description: Kevin and Argit attempt to warn the amalgam kids about the Rooters intentions meanwhile Ben, Rook, and Gwen set off to find Kevin and land themselves in the Null Void!

title: Kitty & Hawk
description: When Puppycorn's favorite toy goes missing, Unikitty & Hawkodile team up to track down the thief, buddy-cop style! But when things get tough and the case goes cold, now it's not just their partnership on the line, but their friendship!

title: Lunch
description: Bing and Sula are chefs today and helping Amma and Flop make lunch. It's Sula's favourite - Easy Peasy Pasta! But, what happens when lunch is served and Bing sees all the ingredients mixed up together?

title: Honey
description: Blippi and FETCH shrink down and fly inside a very active beehive, where they meet Bijon, the fast-talking, fast-moving Worker Bee. With a talent for rhyming and making honey, Bijon rhymes her way through the sweet explanation of how delicious honey is made. What a very buzzy... erm...busy day!

title: Gotta Get Grup to Get Down
description: Grup hires the Warriors to help him become the biggest music star in Rhyboflaven, yet helping the little dragon achieve his big dream is no small task.

title: You Remind Me of Someone
description: Ben and Gwen look for the infamous Bojamboo (the Bigfoot of the South) and discover that it's actually the Forgeti, at the same time as Kevin 11, but when Ben and Kevin are blasted with the Forgeti's forgetfulness mist, they reverse roles and it's up to Gwen and Max to restore them back to normal.

title: The Boys Are Back in Town
description: Him brings the Rowdyruff Boys back, protecting them from the girls' feminine wiles.

title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: Potion in the Ocean
description: Witchy Simone joins the Warriors on a mission deep in the Fickle Sea to find an eye of newt for her magic potion, but Man Fish the Fish Man won't let them harm his sea newt pal!

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Ren Faire
description: Clarence and his pals venture to the Aberdale Renaissance Faire. Clarence confuses a medieval play for reality, and vows to stop the evil black knight from getting the princess.

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: Uncle Zombie
description: Pizza Steve keeps Uncle Grandpa awake all night with terrifying consequences.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: El Peor Rescate de la Historia
description: Los Ninjas intentan rescatar a Cole, pero las discusiones entre prisioneros alertan al Hechicero Calavera, y hace prisioneros a los otros Ninjas.

title: The Perfect Adventure
description: When Mao Mao gets hungry for the perfect adventure, Adorabat tells a white lie.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Ghost Camp/Boo/Never Boop a Robot
description: When Lucas and friends go camping, Avocado tells a scary story. Lucas now thinks there's a ghost in the garden./ Lucas loves to give his friends a scare on Halloween./ When Lucas boops a robot, he and his friends are chased around House!

title: Un Golpe de Ternura
description: Después de derrotar a Strata, Los Fantásticos se dan cuenta de que no volvieron solos, sino con un Bakugan parecido a un panda que les dará muchos problemas.

title: Mine
description: Bing and Pando are on their way home from the beach! And when Pando goes back to Bing's house to collect Bullabaloo, they decide to play one last game before bedtime - Hide and Seek. But where will Pando hide?

title: Fun Proof
description: Apple and Onion want to become this week's "Most Fun People".

title: Ben 10 vs. Negative 10 Part 2
description: Ben, Max and Gwen put up an Alamo like stand inside the bunker at Mount Rushmore and against great odds take down the Forever King's band of baddies. In the end, Ben goes Upchuck and digests the powerful energy source, preventing the Forever King from using it for nefarious purposes. However this ultimate baddie is able to disappear...perhaps to return once again.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Saturday School
description: After creating an unapproved mural on a wall at Aberdale Elementary, Clarence, Jeff and Sumo are forced to come to school on a Saturday to clean up as punishment.

title: Oozing Talent
description: When Sugar unwittingly wins a job as spokesperson for a diarrhea medication, she enlists the help of her friends to stop the commercial from premiering during the big game.

title: The Two Blades
description: In order to escape the Skull Sorcerer's chain-gang, the ninja must convince the Munce and Geckles to put aside their distrust and work together… by promising them something they may not be able to deliver -- The Blades of Deliverance!

title: The Need for Feed/The Zipline Sisters of Treetop Woods
description: MacBarm is bringing food to his hungry chickens, that is, until all of the food falls out of his truck./Grandma and her twin sister want to recreate their old zipline act, but quickly discover that the zipline no longer exists!

title: The Rooters of All Evil
description: Meet the Rooters, the Black Ops wing of the Plumbers from the Null Void. They've come looking for someone close to Ben, and they mean business!

title: Sin Atajos
description: Tras esforzarse por mantener el ritmo en las batallas, Adorabat consigue una armadura cibernética. ¿Pero podrán unos nuevos y sofisticados poderes compensar la falta de experiencia?

title: Shintaro
description: Los Ninjas están invitados a asistir a la fiesta de cumpleaños de la princesa Vania en la ciudad de Shintaro. Llevan al Maestro Wu que está deprimido.

title: The Littlest Tweety
description: Tweety is tired of being overlooked because of his diminutive size.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: The Vengers
description: Billy Billions, Kangaroo Kommando, and Captain Nemesis team up to take down Ben, and claim his place as protector of Bellwood?!?

title: Juntos Solos
description: Steven organiza una fiesta para reunir a su familia.

title: Piernas del Planeta Madre
description: Steven viaja para visitar a su familia.

title: Fan or Foe
description: When Elder Con comes to the Creek, Craig, Kelsey and JP each have a con experience they'll never forget.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: #TweenTitans
description: Jessica Cruz is hired by billionaire playboy Bruce Wayne to chaperone young Dick Grayson's Metropolis birthday bash and brings Karen Beecher along to help, but the girls get more than they bargained for when the tween party guests reveal their titanic personalities.

title: Adrenalandia Junior
description: El equipo de Tennyson visita la versión segura de Adrenalandia, conocida como "Adrenalandia Jr", y allí terminan enfrentándose a un Kevin 11 amargado y decidido a destruir la diversión segura de todos los demás.

title: Into the Dark
description: When Cole investigates a mysterious visitor, the ninja aren't sure what to believe. Cole is frustrated with this lack of team support, until Princess Vania reveals a secret entrance that leads to an underground mine beneath Shintaro - where the city's dark secrets are held.

title: Campamento Unikitty
description: La pandilla está lista para un fin de semana increíble, para vivir la buena vida acampando con estilo en la divertida y amigable naturaleza. Pero cuando Halcondrilo desafía su idea de acampar (debería ser una lucha por la supervivencia en los bosques hostiles), la pandilla intercambia el lugar con él: ahora, Halcondrilo vive una vida de campamento glamoroso mientras Unikitty y los otros sobreviven en la naturaleza. ¿Seguirá creyendo Unikitty que la "increíble naturaleza" es tan increíble si encuentran su destrucción por causas naturales?

title: Familiar
description: Con tantos cambios en su vida, Steven intenta encontrar su lugar en el mundo.

title: Game Over
description: Unagami breaks into the real world and terrorizes Ninjago City while Jay, Zane and Pixal attempt to prevent disaster by reuniting Unagami with his creator, Milton Dyer.

title: Picnic Puzzle
description: Pocoyo and Elly have organized a picnic and they leave Pato in charge of guarding the sandwiches while they get everything ready. Incredibly the sandwiches suddenly start moving around. Pato can't believe his eyes. When Pocoyo and Elly return they are angry with Pato. They think he took the sandwiches himself. They give him one more chance, leaving him in charge of guarding the cake. Once again, amazingly, the cake runs away apparently on its own. Pato is once again berated by Pocoyo and Elly until they see what's going on with their own eyes. Pocoyo investigates further and discovers who it is that's moving the food around: ANTS! Having worked out what's going on, the friends invite the ants along to the picnic and they all have fun together.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Que Rima Con Omnitrix?
description: En un recital de lectura de poesía, Charmcaster lee poemas de Kevin y les causa problemas mágicos a Ben y Gwen cuando produce intercambios mentales que dejan a todos confundidos acerca de quién pelea contra quién.

title: Baby Bird Sitting
description: When Sleepy Bird has to pop out for a while, she needs someone to look after little Baby Bird. Pato volunteers because he thinks that's going to be a much easier job than tidying up the mess he's made with Pocoyo. Baby Bird, and his chum Caterpillar, run rings round Pato who eventually appeals to Pocoyo for help. Pocoyo thinks he can take care of the situation easily himself, but he similarly is foxed by the little tykes. Finally Pocoyo and Pato work out that in order to get the little ones to do what they want, they are going to need to collaborate. By the time Sleepy Bird returns, Baby Bird and Caterpillar are fast asleep. Little does Sleepy Bird know the chaos that got them to that point!

title: #EmperorPenguin
description: When Barbara Gordon attempts to do something nice for a friend, she ends up in the clutches of the Penguin, a high school mob boss who blackmails her into an increasingly desperate situation from which only Batgirl can save her.

title: Shintaro
description: The ninja are invited to attend the birthday party of Princess Vania, in the distant Kingdom of Shintaro. They depart, bringing along Master Wu, unaware that he is feeling his age…

title: Woof
description: Bing and Flop are in the park, when a doggie called Sunshine comes to play catch with them! Bing loves playing with Sunshine, but what will happen when Bing realises he can't keep Sunshine?

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Wasteland
description: After Uncle Grandpa neglects his garbage duties, he embarks on a quest to save his friends from the overflowing pile of trash.

title: Valley of the Shamrocks
description: When Grumpy replaces mission navigator Good Luck with a computerized navigational gadget, Good Luck feels useless -- until he saves the Valley of the Shamrocks and is proclaimed a hero by the Whiffles, who don't want him to leave. He is torn between staying with the Whiffles and remaining with the Bears.

title: Gyranoid of the Future
description: Apple and Onion are dead set on riding Gyranoid of the Future, the craziest roller coaster at the carnival.

title: Everyone's Present
description: Wow… Presents! One for Pocoyo, one for Elly and one for Pato! How exciting. Pocoyo's present is some string, Pato gets some paper and Elly some sticks. They have fun for a while, each playing with their own present in a bid to prove that it's the best of the bunch. But ultimately the friends get a little bored with their respective gifts. After all, there's only so much you can do with one thing. In a huff, the friends throw their new toys on the floor. And this is when they see the potential of the presents: they can combine them. They put the presents together to make a kite. Wonderful, something they can all play with together.

title: Kabums Part 2
description: Inspirados por la película "Bebés vs. perros", los Titanes deciden hacer una gran película de Hollywood propia.

title: Election Day
description: In an effort to prove to Master Frown that she is no tyrant, Unikitty agrees to hold an election to see who will be the new princess of the Unikingdom. In a shock, Master Frown takes an early lead in the poles. Unikitty discovers Frown is winning because he's cheating. Will she resort to her own dirty tricks to win the election or stay true to her self and try to win by being nice?

title: Bubbles of the Opera
description: When Bubbles gets a bad school photo, it sends her into an existential tailspin of darkness.

title: The BFFS
description: Gumball's old BFF Fuzzy, turns up on his doorstep. Darwin struggles to accept that there was someone before him and fails to contain his jealousy. But is Darwin right to mistrust Fuzzy? Does Fuzzy actually have sinister motives for reconnecting with his old BFF?

title: Seed No Evil/City of Clipsville
description: Seed No Evil: When a prehistoric caveman thaws out in Townsville, the girls must stop him from stealing the Mayor's seeds./City of Clipsville: The girls reminisce on their adventures in these new, never-before-seen clips!

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: La Inquisicion
description: El superintendente escolar Malo visita la Secundaria Elmore para erradicar cualquier conducta caricaturesca.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Not Yours
description: Bing's helping Flop pick up groceries in Padget's shop today. And while Flop is paying, Bing picks up a lolly and puts it in his pocket. But what happens when Flop explains to Bing that he has stolen the lolly?

title: Adrenaland Jr.
description: Team Tennyson visits the safety-neutered version of Adrenaland known as "Adrenaland Jr.", only to end up facing off against a bitter Kevin 11, out to destroy everyone else's good, and safe, time.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Gut Feelings
description: With help from Zombie Pumpkin Magisword, the Warriors help get to the root of who stole all the vegetable Magiswords that belong to the angry bunny, Hoppus.

title: Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

title: Bubble
description: Panda becomes a germophobe and decides to live the rest of his life in a bubble.

title: No Shortcuts
description: After struggling to keep up, Adorabat gets a cybernetic "Mega-Mech." But can fancy new powers make up for experience?

title: Pijamada sin Dormir
description: Hay una fiesta de pijamas en el castillo, y Unikitty y Perricornio quieren quedarse despiertos toda la noche, porque creen que algo mágico debe suceder si te quedas despierto el tiempo suficiente. Al principio, los amigos están dispuestos a quedarse despiertos toda la noche. Pero cuando comienzan a quedarse dormidos de a uno, ia Unikitty le preocupa que no lo logren! ¿Hasta dónde llegarán ella y su hermano para mantenerse despiertos, y descubrirán la razón secreta por la que se supone que la gente debe irse a la cama cuando aparece El Arenero?

title: Me Recuerdas a Alguien
description: Ben y Gwen buscan al tristemente célebre Bojamboo (el Pie Grande del Sur) y descubren que en realidad se trata del Olvideti.

title: Boo-Dunnit
description: When the box goes missing at a haunted mansion, the Bears play detective to help uncover the thief.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Married and Broke
description: Muscle Man and Starla want to win a game show to pay for their wedding.

title: The Worst Rescue Ever
description: The ninja attempt to rescue Cole, but the bickering of his fellow prisoners, the Geckles and Munce, alerts the Skull Sorcerer, and soon the ninja are prisoners too.

title: Pruebas de Diversion
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren convertirse en la "Gente más divertida" de esta semana.

title: That's the Way the Windmill Blows!/Mecha Machine Makers!
description: The windmill isn't turning, which means Sunny Field Farm has no power. The windmill needs to turn again so Zee can launch his rocket!/Izzy and Timmy are making a bird caller for Grandma, but have trouble connecting pieces of their machine.

title: Ghost Train
description: Percy has to deliver the mail on Halloween when everyone knows the legendary Ghost Train comes out! Thomas rolls along to help Percy face his fears, but when a "real" Ghost Train appears... things get almost spooky.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go
